{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10106701988329-2":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10106701988329-2","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[{"id":"KP_10100096575182","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]},{"id":"KP_10100096598780","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]},{"id":"KP_10100096795659","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]}],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100074586783-4","P_10100074586783-5","P_10100074586783-6"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读课外短文，完成练习","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":660,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>如果麦子没有考验</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">①上帝看到果实累累，感到非常开心。一个在麦田里的农夫认出了他，上前向上帝请安：“仁慈的上帝呀，你终于来了。这50年来，我没有一天停止祈祷<sup><span style=\";vertical-align:super\">①</span></sup>，期盼着你的降临，你终于来了。”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">②上帝说：“50年来，你都在祈祷，到底在祈祷什么呢？”<br></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">③“我总是在祈求风调雨顺，祈祷今年不要有大风雨，不要下雪，不要地震，不要干旱，不要有冰雹，不要有虫害，可是无论我怎么祈祷，总是不能如愿！”农夫说。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">④农夫跪下来，吻上帝的脚：“全能的主呀！可不可以在明年允诺我的请求，只要一年的时间，不要风，不要雨，不要烈日与灾害，别人的田我不管。能不能给我一年的时间？”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">⑤上帝说：“好吧！明年如你所愿。”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">⑥第二年，农夫的田地果然结出许多麦穗，由于没有任何狂风、暴雨、烈日与灾害，麦穗比平常多一倍，农夫兴奋不已，欢天喜地地等待收成的那一天。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">⑦到了收成的时刻，（奇怪　惊喜）的事情发生了，农夫的麦穗里（竟然　果然）没有结出一粒麦子。</p>       <p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">⑧农夫找到了上帝，问道：“仁慈的上帝，这是怎么一回事，是不是搞错了某些部分?”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">⑨上帝说：“我没有搞错任何事情。一旦避开了所有的考验，麦子就变得无能了。<span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">对于一粒麦子，努力奋斗是不可避免的。风雨是必要的，烈日是必要的，蝗虫是必要的，它们可以唤醒麦子内在的灵魂；人的灵魂也和麦子的灵魂相同，如果没有任何考验，人也只有一个空壳罢了。”</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">注释：</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">①祈祷：一种宗教意识，信仰宗教的人向神默告自己的愿望。</p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"<p>选出恰当的词语。</p><p>（ ）的事情发生了</p>","answers":[{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[{"id":"KP_10100076190450","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]}],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000631040","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"word","options":[{"option":"奇怪","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"惊喜","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101006],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]},{"content":"<p>选出恰当的词语。</p><p>麦穗里（ ）没有结出一粒麦子。</p>","answers":[{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000631040","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"word","options":[{"option":"竟然","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"果然","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"begi